<TITLE> Overseas treatment for mayor, but no Umrah </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Chittagong, Oct 15 (bdnews24.com)Bailed mayor A B M Mohiuddin Chowdhury has been allowed to go abroad for treatment, his lawyer said Wednesday. Lawyer Harisadhan Deb Burman told reporters that a letter signed by a local government ministry official reached the mayor at 10pm. Burman said the government gave him 45 days for overseas treatment, but did not grant his petition to go to Saudia Arabia to perform Umrah. bd
